data.description: Don't miss this 3 bedroom, 2 bath home in Mustang School District. Easy access to I-40, being just minutes away from Shopping, food and entertainment. Home features spacious bedrooms, with built-in desk, Storm shelter and small area for your pets to stay out of the weather. You will love the large workshop in back with garage style door and electricity. Extra wide driveway that wraps around the side of the home, creating a great area to park a boat or camper. Easy to show, come check out your new home today.
